name": "Screenshot_Rogue_01.png", "id": "24178243448488031", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75334061_24178243461821363_8444984069212333615_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=QQ17vtbCv4AQ7kNvgGP5FyR&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAjM3j-hp_gTFhI030XLs0ctwi6WVCTkORd9Gyu4JhvPw&oe=670914A4"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_PsyOps_01.png", "id": "377395914625685", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974858_377395917959018_3593137405102898192_n.png?_nc_cat=104&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=VE1DzLoMlqEQ7kNvgHaEgpJ&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBbSES399Ja6H1fffJn9VLpPO7LJs6zxAhJcwKisg0j1Q&oe=6708F444"}, {"file_name": "Screenshot_Bridge_01.png", "id": "1031201894811272", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/75520121_1031201898144605_7374826040376756589_n.png?_nc_cat=111&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=JLAdiOOi0-UQ7kNvgFZFRUE&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAq4S41s4Bpqlkx7YKweAu4OhUHAJbV31NhW3q8K0YQOg&oe=67091CE3"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "RogueKey_land2.png", "id": "770369555207447", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38984474_770369558540780_2842347539423012743_n.png?_nc_cat=110&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=mwqkxDy22xIQ7kNvgFG-MXI&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAs-G9Swqc6tl9jMB3M6e34Jq9Nh5VI59xKlnOO7IJfUw&oe=670920BB"}, "display_name": "Rogue Ascent VR", "keywords": ["handtracking", "roguelike", "rogue", "scifi", "shooter"], "long_description": "\n# \ud83d\udc49Save the World with Finger Guns\n\nRogue Ascent VR is a roguelike shooter specially developed for Meta Quest hand-tracking technology.\n\nEquip, craft, and upgrade as you fight to save your homeworld from destruction!\n\n{309379285531879}\n\nBlast your way through a hostile space station with intuitive motion controls -- never lifting a controller\n- Make finger guns to shoot\n- Block with your fists\n- Reach out to dash around\n- Control the action entirely with your hands\n\nDynamic bosses chambers, unique character interactions, NPC companions, and online leaderboards will challenge you in new ways for every run.\n\nTwitch Integration allows the audience to help (or hinder) a streamer\u2019s run by spawning items, throwing confetti, and even hiring bounty hunters!\n- Everything is customizable, so it's up to each streamer to choose what their viewers can and can't unleash.\n\n================================\n\n# \ud83d\udee0\ufe0fSandbox Update\n\nYou can now control the pace of the action -- Rogue Ascent\u2019s new sandbox mode lets you experiment with every element of the game\u2019s hand-tracking combat. \n\nPlayers will be given access to a huge training facility equipped with weapon modding stations, quick-play scenarios, and NPC customization terminals. \n\nSerious or silly, The Sandbox is a space to get creative and test your talent. Here are a few of the new features you can expect to find in The Sandbox.\n\n- New NPCS\n- Sandbox Settings\n- Scenario Kiosks\n- Unlocked Crafting Tables\n- Unlocked Item Vending Shop", "short_description": "Save the World with Finger Guns\n\nRogue Ascent VR is a roguelike shooter specially developed for Meta Quest hand-tracking technology.\n"}]}, "developer_name": "Nooner Bear Studio LLC", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.clique.games/privacy-policy/", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.clique.games/terms-and-conditions", "publisher_name": "Clique Games LLC", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://rogueascent.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_SOME", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1436351953220286"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "ARCADE", "SHOOTER"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED_